; Regression test for issue #1142: ledger --base -X 'h=3600s' bal report everything in hours (BZ#1142)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1142
; The --base flag combined with -X 'h=3600s' should convert all time amounts (in seconds)
; to hours in the balance report.

2024/01/01 Work session
    Time:Work    7200s
    Income:Time

2024/01/01 Work session
    Time:Work    3600s
    Income:Time

test --base -X 'h=3600s' bal
              -3.00h  Income:Time
               3.00h  Time:Work
--------------------
                   0
end test
